diamondsByClarity <- diamonds %>%
    group_by(clarity) %>%
    summarise(mean_price = mean(price),
              median_price = median(price),
              min_price = min(price),
              max_price = max(price),
              n = n())
head(diamondsByClarity)

##   clarity mean_price median_price min_price max_price     n

diamondsByColor <- diamonds %>%
    group_by(color) %>%
    summarise(mean_price = mean(price),
              median_price = median(price),
              min_price = min(price),
              max_price = max(price),
              n = n())
head(diamondsByColor)

p1 <- ggplot(aes(x = color, y = mean_price), data = diamondsByColor) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity")

p2 <- ggplot(aes(x = clarity, y = mean_price), data = diamondsByClarity) +
    geom_bar(stat="identity")

grid.arrange(p1, p2, ncol = 1)
